data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home that could be yours built by LBK AND BEST OF ALL NO HOA! This home has an excellent farm style at the New Bittersweet Subdivision in Springtown. IT SITS ON A ONE ACRE LOT, has a great curb appeal with a warm inviting foyer and an open concept, the center island is accompanied by stainless steel appliances. The Master bedroom comes with separate vanities, a large garden tub, separate shower and a large walk in closet. It also has 2 fireplaces and a large outside patio to entertain your family and friends.The perimeter walls are foam insulated to help with energy efficiency. Come see this beautiful home close to nearby Springtown schools. Do not miss out on this opportunity to check out this stunning home waiting for its next family. Neither seller or listing agent make any warranties or representation as to accuracy of the data listed. Please do your own due diligence and verify all information, schools and restrictions.
